-- German Industry Chamber Sees No Recession Danger, Bild Reports
-- B y   J e f f   B l a c k
-- 2012-01-02T07:52:58Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-01-02/german-industry-chamber-sees-no-recession-danger-bild-reports.html
The German Chamber of Industry and
Commerce DIHK doesn’t see any immediate danger of recession,
 Bild  newspaper reported, citing a briefing.  While the DIHK expects “zero” growth for the fourth
quarter of 2011 and the first three months of 2012, the economy
won’t go into reverse, the newspaper reported.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Jeff Black in Frankfurt at 
 jblack25@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
